<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-21-1070 </DOCNO><TEXT>Nuclear analytical techniques, like neutron activation analysis and passivegamma spectrometry, have been adjusted to cover a variety of applications,like exploration of mineral and energy resources, geochemistry, environmentalcontrol, biomedicine, industrial and agricultural quality control, archaeometryetc. For certain applications, like nuclear safeguards analysis and referencematerial certification of uranium samples, special techniques based onthe delayed neutron counting method have been developed in order to achivethe required accuracy.</TEXT></DOC>